SectionBody.Text: Except as expressly provided in this act:

Subsection.Text: With respect to any wastewater facility privatization contract entered into under this act, a public entity is subject to s. 125.3401, s. 180.301, s. 189.423, or s. 190.0125 but is not subject to the requirements of chapter 287.

A wastewater facility subject to a wastewater facility privatization contract made under this act shall continue to be regulated for all local, state, and federal purposes as if owned, operated, and maintained by the public entity.
